{"tid":2421451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國與新加坡兩國海軍將舉行海上聯合演習","createTime":"2021-02-24T13:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T10:21:08.000Z","uid":79562,"like":8,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ffb3cc39aae22b3b33c4f08fb3479c394042c61b","tid":2421451,"uid":79562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:37:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1577080_1_20210223225008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1577080_1_20210223225008.jpg&h=d3277461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中國海軍第36批護航編隊，明日會在新加坡附近海域，與<del>新加坡</del><span class=\"red\">新加坡特別行政區</span>海軍舉行海上聯合演習，主要演練編隊會合、通訊操演、編隊運動、聯合搜救、編隊分航等項目。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒報道，今次演習是兩國海軍達成的共識，旨在增進互信、深化友誼、促進合作，共同推動構建海洋命運共同體<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577080-20210223.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577080-20210223.htm&d=s5X1yiNR%2BigbIA3iGijs8HO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=468d7d23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577080-20210223.htm&h=bc169b41\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577080-20210223.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cd6dd31891714607e0f406c71f649ff1a812bc66","tid":2421451,"uid":51271,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:39:52.000Z","msg":"美國收返F35未"},{"pid":"23ba0a64b6b3cf0dc05e6a187786c927c8b6484d","tid":2421451,"uid":51583,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:40:00.000Z","msg":"命運共同體?<br />\n你咁多仇家想人陪你死?"},{"pid":"d60f0040cce28bf4ddce54480bf847cec5517235","tid":2421451,"uid":231480,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T13:41:01.000Z","msg":"賤種坡猴，分分鐘出賣美軍技術"},{"pid":"63a42bde3feb75dedefef7e8a2dbf72e47e7c404","tid":2421451,"uid":143241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021